{"id":"5e9c2b4a9b6559241525d54c","artists":["5e9b68d47a1236eccfeb1e73"],"title":"News: Blood Red Shoes Announce New LP And Stream A New Track","content":"<p>Brighton based duo <strong>Blood Red Shoes</strong> have just announced details of their third LP set to be released 26 March 2012 via <strong>V2/Cooperative Music</strong>.</p><p> The record, entitled <em><strong>In Time To Voices</strong></em> is their first since 2010’s <strong>Fire Like This</strong>, and the group, comprised of drummer<strong> Steven Ansell</strong> and guitarist <strong>Laura-Mary Carter</strong> have also made a new track available for streaming via their website. Cold is a heavily percussion led affair, with a brooding guitar riff laboring throughout the track, as <strong>Ansell</strong> and <strong>Carter</strong> continuously swap vocal duties. They’ve also announced details of a full UK tour, which you can see the dates for below. Check out <em>Cold</em> below and pre-order<em><strong> In Time To Voices</strong></em> via the <strong>Blood Red Shoes</strong> <a href=\"https://www.bloodredshoes.co.uk/home/\" target=\"_blank\">website</a>.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jNIdZFKxFLM\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\"></iframe><a href=\"https://api.crackintheroad.com/music/14393-news-blood-red-shoes-announce-new-lp-and-stream-a-new-track/attachment/332773_10150471888331307_9059291306_8924306_15314969_o/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-14396\"><img class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-14396\" style=\"margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 50px;\" title=\"Blood Red Shoes Tour\" src=\"https://admin.crackintheroad.com/uploads/2012/01/332773_10150471888331307_9059291306_8924306_15314969_o-640x536.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"536\" /></a> </p>\n","slug":"14393-news-blood-red-shoes-announce-new-lp-and-stream-a-new-track","category":"music","date":1327433531000,"wpid":14393,"isSticky":false,"featured_image":{"width":165,"height":110,"src":"2012/01/329551_1015039536